Since $PT$ and $QR$ are parallel, then $\angle TPQ$ and $\angle PQR$ are supplementary. Thus, $\angle PQR + 64^\circ = 180^\circ,$ so $\angle PQR = \boxed{116} \text{ degrees}.$

